		  INSTALLATION INSTRUCTION FOR IRC II V1.70

1. Using your favorite editor, modify the config.h file to meet your
site specifications.  Instructions for doing this are included in the
config.h file.

2.  Again using your favorite editor, modify the Makefile to meet
your site specifications regarding program and help file
installation.  If you are compiling for an HPUX system, you will have
to change the LIBS variable in the Makefile as well.

3. Type "make install".




